#: hat/templates/dashboard/home.html:21
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Programme National de Lutte contre la Trypanosomiase Humaine Africaine (PNLTHA) of the DRC Ministry of Health drives the programme to diagnose, treat and reduce HAT cases in the DRC.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Republique Democratique du Congo, Ministere de la Santé Publique, Programme National de Lutte contre la THA (PNLTHA)."

#: hat/templates/dashboard/home.html:32
msgid "Map showing pilot health zones"
msgstr "Carte montrant les zones de santé pilotes"

#: hat/templates/dashboard/home.html:35
msgid "Programme Mission"
msgstr "Mission du Programme"

#: hat/templates/dashboard/home.html:37
msgid ""
"\n"
"        To coordinate and organise the strugge against HAT in RD Congo\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Coordonner et Organiser la lutte contre la THA en R.D.Congo"

#: hat/templates/dashboard/home.html:41
msgid "Programme Objective"
msgstr "Objectif du Programme"

#: hat/templates/dashboard/home.html:43
msgid ""
"\n"
"        To reduce the morbidity and mortality due to HAT to a level compatible with a normal productive life for the inhabitants of areas where the disease is endemic (1 case per 10,000 inhabitants)\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Réduire la morbidité et la mortalité due au THA à un niveau compatible avec une vie productive normale pour les habitants des zones où la maladie est endémique (1 cas par 10000 habitants)"

#: hat/templates/dashboard/home.html:47
msgid "Programme Organisation"
msgstr "Organisation du Programme"

#: hat/templates/dashboard/home.html:49
